{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"Hello, please help me\", \"role\": \"user\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Hello! I'm Sculptor, an AI coding agent powered by Claude Code. I'm here to help you with your coding tasks.\\n\\nLet me first check what we're working with in your repository.\", \"type\": \"text\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_01R5j6wi1ohw6MSr3f3KCMp2\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"pwd\", \"description\": \"Check current working directory\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_01S4dYsbhY4oBdhwc1NGo7CW\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"ls -la\", \"description\": \"List files in current directory\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}], \"role\": \"assistant\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01CkixQDKou38WTjhLS2Xbe1", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I can see you have a repository with:\n- A `src` directory\n- A `data` directory  \n- `README.md`, `.gitignore`, and `stuff.txt` files\n- You're currently on branch `branch_1`\n\nHow can I help you today? I can:\n- Write or modify code\n- Fix bugs\n- Refactor existing code\n- Answer questions about your codebase\n- Add new features\n- Review code\n- Help with git operations\n\nWhat would you like me to work on?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 8, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 808, "cache_read_input_tokens": 15294, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 808, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 120, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
